org.cpsolver.studentsct.online

Class OnlineSection

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.ifs.assignment.context.AbstractClassWithContext<Request,Enrollment,Section.SectionContext>
      • org.cpsolver.studentsct.model.Section
        • org.cpsolver.studentsct.online.OnlineSection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Section>, AssignmentComparable<Section,Request,Enrollment>, CanHoldContext, CanInheritContext<Request,Enrollment,Section.SectionContext>, HasAssignmentContext<Request,Enrollment,Section.SectionContext>, SctAssignment

    public class OnlineSection
extends Section
    An online section. A simple extension of the Section class that allows to set the current section enrollment. This class is particularly useful when a model containing only the given student is constructed (to provide him/her with a schedule or suggestions).
    Version:
